== Introduction

  This project is an attempt to clean up some of the pitfalls of tagging.

== Features

   For now, all features are to be used within script/console:

    1. Edit trees in a text file:  @node.text_update
    2. View tag trees

== Install
  
  1. Install necessary gems: `rake gems:install`
  2. Copy config/database.yml.example to config/database.yml and setup your db.
  2. Run migrations: `rake db:migrate`
